---

[Example Usage - CLI call to OpenClaw]
# Manual trigger:
curl -X POST http://127.0.0.1:18789/api/agents/content-writer/run \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d '{
    "brand": "DFROBOT",
    "product_full_name": "DFR0868 Beetle Board Kit ESP32-C3-MINI-1 RISC-V",
    "part_number": "DFR0868",
    "sku": "MCU-ESP-DFR-BEETLE-C3",
    "category": "MCU",
    "raw_specs": "...(paste raw specs)...",
    "kit_contents": "Beetle ESP32-C3 x1, Expansion board x1, Pin connector x1",
    "datasheet_url": "http://www.farnell.com/datasheets/4020603.pdf"
  }'

# Webhook trigger from bs4u-tech middleware:
# POST https://pwd.bs4u-tech.com/api/content/generate
# Body: { product_id: "123", source: "odoo" }
# → middleware fetches raw data from Odoo + D1 → calls OpenClaw → saves to Odoo
---
